Speaker 1: Okay, thank you, sir. Can you just confirm your date of birth for me?

Speaker 2: It is 7-31-1959.

Speaker 1: Okay, thanks. I have your account here.

Speaker 2: And I just wanted to let you know that we're not a subscription.

Speaker 1: Actually, we're a telehealth.

Speaker 2: So that prescription that your doctor approved comes available with refills.

Speaker 1: And as our customer, you can actually set it up however you want,

Speaker 2: whatever frequency and quantity you want.

Speaker 1: And you can always modify that at any time as well.

Speaker 2: Or put a pause on your account for up to six months.

Speaker 1: I do recommend keeping your prescription active with refills and not canceling it.

Speaker 2: Otherwise, when you want to place a future order with us,

Speaker 1: you won't be able to because we won't have a prescription to send to the pharmacy.

Speaker 2: So for now, did you want me to put a pause on your account

Speaker 1: or set it up for refills every four months, every five months?

Speaker 2: Let's put a pause on it.

Speaker 1: And to get new pills, do I have to physically call?

Speaker 2: What I'll do is I'll put a pause on it until July.

Speaker 1: That way you'll have plenty of time to try it out, see how you like it for yourself,

Speaker 2: and then you can call us and let us know how you want to set it up going forward.

Speaker 1: Like I said, we have customers that get their refills every month,

Speaker 2: and we have some that get it every six months and everything in between.

Speaker 1: It's really up to you.

Speaker 2: And at any time, we understand that circumstances in life change.

Speaker 1: You can pause your account at any given time for up to six months.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: So what time in July is that pause still?

Speaker 2: Like the 1st of July?

Speaker 1: Nope, July 23rd.

Speaker 2: July 23rd.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: So call you back either before then or with a refill or no refill?

Speaker 1: Yes, you can call before then if you want to place an order.

Speaker 2: And you can also, when you call us, you can set up your account however you want.

Speaker 1: You can extend that hold or you can set it up for refills that you're liking.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Yes, I will see how everything works and get back with you then.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Sounds great.

Speaker 2: Thank you for calling in.

Speaker 1: I'm excited for you to try the new AGD.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: Thank you.
